translation.Name: Buak_Note_17
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: I’ve just been given the opportunity of a lifetime. I am now the newest franchise owner of Scorpion-7 Laboratories, I get to run my own facility! Where did I choose, well, British Columbia of course! Nothing like the familiar scent of home. Everyone who would work with me was in accord since they get to be closer to their homes, too. Tomorrow, I’ll be travelling out to B.C. to pick out the best suitable land candidate so that we start construction A.S.A.P.
